Subject:    <a href="?t=95837889000006&r=1&w=2">Re: [Paul Richards &lt;richards%shangrila.cs.uiuc.edu@a.cs.uiuc.edu&gt;: Bogus ROOT domain server on ARPAn</a>
From:       <a href="?a=95837784400016&r=1&w=2">hedrick () topaz ! rutgers ! edu (Charles Hedrick)</a>
