[Download RAW <a href="?l=namedroppers&m=95837781926878&q=mbox">message</a> or <a href="?l=namedroppers&m=95837781926878&q=raw">body</a>]</b>

My view is that the root servers should always be specified in
initialization files, and the resolvers should not enter values that
somebody else tells them into their cache.  People are going to make
mistakes in setting up software.  The system can't be such that a
mistake at one site has this kind of disasterous effect on other sites.

